stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> DepositDetected : blockchain-monitor publishes DEPOSIT_DETECTED

    DepositDetected --> DepositConfirmed : confirmations >= threshold\nDEPOSIT_CONFIRMED published

    DepositConfirmed --> SagaStarted : SagaOrchestrator.execute()

    SagaStarted --> ConfirmDepositStep : Step 1 - confirm_deposit
    ConfirmDepositStep --> LiquidityReservationStep : Step 2 - reserve_liquidity

    LiquidityReservationStep --> PaymentSchedulingStep : Step 3 - schedule_payments
    PaymentSchedulingStep --> SagaCompleted : all steps succeeded

    SagaCompleted --> PaymentDue : SecureJobScheduler polls due payments
    PaymentDue --> PaymentExecuted : PAYMENT_EXECUTED published
    PaymentExecuted --> [*]

    ConfirmDepositStep --> Compensating : Step 1 failed
    LiquidityReservationStep --> Compensating : Step 2 failed
    PaymentSchedulingStep --> Compensating : Step 3 failed

    Compensating --> CompensateReserveLiquidity : compensate reserve_liquidity
    CompensateReserveLiquidity --> CompensateConfirmDeposit : compensate confirm_deposit
    CompensateConfirmDeposit --> Compensated

    Compensating --> Failed : compensation itself failed

    Compensated --> [*]
    Failed --> [*]
